%20and%20mash%3C%2Fa%3E)%20are%20very%20different%20in%20texture%20and%20flavor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%20for%20me%2C%20a%20local%20helped%20me%20find%20an%20Italian%20marketplace%20in%20Central%20London%2C%20where%20the%20sausages%20were%20excellent%20(and%20similar%20to%20what%20I%20had%20back%20home)%2C%20just%20quite%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22008a38d8-daad-43b2-b60e-75f6e0f417ef%5C%22%3EThe%20hours%20of%20operation%20are%20shorter%20than%20what%20I%20was%20used%20to%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAdmittedly%2C%20I%20was%20spoiled%20by%20having%20access%20to%20a%2024-hour%20grocery%20store%20in%20my%20New%20York%20City%20neighborhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20accustomed%20to%20being%20able%20to%20pick%20up%20a%20few%20things%20on%20my%20way%20home%20from%20an%20evening%20out%2C%20or%20to%20occasionally%20capitalize%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravel-reporter-mistake-long-haul-flight-timing-jet-lag-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejet%20lag%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20some%20early%20morning%20shopping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20London%2C%20I%20have%20to%20be%20more%20strategic%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20on%20Sundays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20want%20to%20visit%20a%20Lidl%20or%20Sainsbury's%20on%20a%20Sunday%2C%20I%20only%20have%20a%20short%20window%20to%20do%20so%2C%20as%20the%20shops%20typically%20open%20at%2011%20a.m.%20and%20close%20by%205%20p.m.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a99794be-75a8-4419-822d-3fd5b28ca600%5C%22%3EEggs%20aren't%20located%20in%20the%20refrigerated%20section%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Non-refrigerated%20eggs%20on%20display%20for%20sale%20in%20a%20store%20in%20England.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683f489d9d73a0031e8dca0b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEggs%20aren't%20refrigerated%20at%20grocery%20stores%20in%20the%20UK.%3Cp%3ESteve%20Travelguide%2FShu