ty%2C%20the%20podcast%20used%20Mighty%20Networks.%20It%20also%20has%20a%20licensing%20partnership%20with%20iHeartMedia%2C%20which%20handles%20the%20podcast's%20advertising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCommunity%20really%20has%20always%20been%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20what%20we%20do%20with%20'Therapy%20for%20Black%20Girls%2C'%20specifically%20with%20the%20podcast%2C%26quot%3B%20Harden%20Bradford%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20much%20they%20earn%20from%20Patreon%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20about%20%242%2C000%20in%20May%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20they%20do%20it%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BTherapy%20for%20Black%20Girls%26quot%3B%20offers%20two%20tiers%20on%20Patreon%20%E2%80%94%20one%20is%20%2410%20a%20month%20and%20another%20is%20%2414%20a%20month.%20Paying%20members%20get%20access%20to%20ad-free%20versions%20of%20the%20podcast%2C%20as%20well%20as%20access%20to%20podcast%20episodes%20that%20aren't%20available%20elsewhere%2C%20such%20as%20its%20%26quot%3BSo%20My%20Therapist%20Said%E2%80%A6%26quot%3B%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20definitely%20doing%20content%20release%20drops%20when%20there's%20a%20new%20episode%20of%20one%20of%20our%20segments%2C%26quot%3B%20COO%20Ashley%20Cherry%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20we're%20also%20posting%20outside%20of%20that%20%E2%80%A6%20to%20get%20people%20talking%20in%20the%20comments%20to%20really%20cultivate%20a%20sense%20of%20community.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20higher%20tier%20also%20unlocks%20more%20virtual%20events%20for%20its%20community%2C%20such%20as%20weekly%20check-ins%20where%20members%20can%20talk%20about%20their%20lives%20or%20do%20journaling%20prompts%20together.%20Members%20receive%20perks%20like%20early%20access%20to%20tickets%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finfluencers-in-person-events-build-communities-make-money-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ein-person%20events%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20merch%2C%20and%20giveaways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2296524393-5f39-4577-bd56-5e6100ab7e33%5C%22%3ETrue%20crime%20podcast%20'RedHanded'%20became%20a%20full-time%20job%20for%20its%20cohost%20because%20of%20Patreon.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223291%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22RedHanded%20hosts%20Suruthi%20Bala%20and%20Hannah%20Maguire%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68405fd3c19ab3675c109f8d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222468%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHannah%20Maguire%20and%20Suruthi%20Bala%20cohost%20the%20%26quot%3BRedHanded%26quot%3B%20podcast.%3Cp%3EAlan%20Chapman%2FDave%20Benett%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20it%20is%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BRedHanded%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20true%20crime%20podcast%20hosted%20by%20Suruthi%20Bala%20and%20Hannah%20Maguire%2C%20who%20are%20both%20based%20in%20the%20UK.%20The%20podcast%20launched%20in%202017%20and%20joined%20Patreon%20the%20same%20year.%20Maguire%20told%20BI%20that%20if%20it%20weren't%20for%20the%20podcast's%20earnings%20on%20Patreon%2C%20she%20wouldn't%20have%20been%20able%20to%20quit%20her%20previous%20job%20to%20pursue%20podcasting%20full%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRedHanded%26quot%3B%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Wondery%20podcast%20network%20and%20gets%20paid%20a%20guaranteed%20minimum%20as%20part%20of%20its%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20much%20they%20earn%20from%20Patreon%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20about%20%2459%2C000%20a%20month%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20they%20do%20it%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BRedHanded%26quot%3B%20offers%20three%20tiers%2C%20which%20start%20at%20%244%20a%20month%20and%20go%20up%20to%20%2418%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20spent%20a%20long%20time%2C%20many%20years%2C%20really%20finessing%20the%20tiers%20that%20we%20now%20have%20on%20there%20and%20the%20way%20in%20which%20we%20monetize%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Bala%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lowest%20tier%20unlocks%20ad-free%20episodes%20that%20fans%20can%20listen%20to%20a%20day%20early%2C%20and%20access%20to%20audio%20episodes%20of%20the%20team's%20second%20podcast%20series%2C%20%26quot%3BUnder%20the%20Duvet.%26quot%3B%20The%20middle%20tier%20also%20unlocks%20a%20monthly%20bonus%20episode%20of%20%26quot%3BRedHanded%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20video%20version%20of%20%26quot%3BUnder%20the%20Duvet.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BRedHanded's%26quot%3B%20most%20expensive%20tier%20gives%20subscribers%20access%20to%20the%20podcast's%20full%20library%20of%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRedHanded's%26quot%3B%20Patreon%20accounts%20for%20about%2025%25%20of%20the%20podcasts'%20revenue%20now%2C%20Bala%20estimated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228c6a4576-a4d2-409e-ac1e-71c183c6c52f%5C%22%3EComedy%20podcast%20'The%20Yard'%20earns%206%20figures%20a%20month.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223915%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22LOS%20ANGELES%2C%20CALIFORNIA%20-%20DECEMBER%2007%3A%20Ludwig%20Ahgren%20attends%20The%20Streamer%20Awards%20hosted%20by%20QTCinderella%20at%20The%20Mayan%20on%20December%2007%2C%202024%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20California.%20(Photo%20by%20Jesse%20Grant%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20QTCinderella)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6840b5589b2a601d01b25427%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222936%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELudwig%20Ahgren%20is%20one%20of%20four%20hosts%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BThe%20Yard%26quot%3B%20podcast.%3Cp%3EJesse%20Grant%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20QTCinderella%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20it%20is%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BThe%20Yard%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20podcast%20cohosted%20by%20four%20friends%2C%20including%20Twitch%20streamer%20Ludwig%20Ahgren.%20The%20podcast%20launched%20in%202021%20and%20is%20one%20of%20the%20top%20podcasts%20on%20Patreon%2C%20with%20more%20than%2058%2C000%20members%20%E2%80%94%20about%2037%2C000%20of%20whom%20are%20paid%20subscribers.%20The%20Yard%20is%20part%20of%20The%20Roost%20podcast%20network.%3C%2