0bucket%20of%20water%20just%20to%20clean%20up%20small%20messes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20what%20makes%20the%20Shark%20HydroVac%20Pro%20XL%20Cordless%20hard%20floor%20cleaner%20such%20an%20appealing%20innovation.%20It's%20technically%20a%20vac-mop%2C%20meaning%20both%20a%20vacuum%20and%20mop%20rolled%20into%20one%2C%20and%20its%20cordless%20design%20takes%20care%20of%20all%20the%20hard%20work%2C%20automatically%20dispensing%20cleaning%20solution%20and%20scrubbing%20your%20floors%20with%20hundreds%20of%20rotations%20a%20minute.%20I%20wanted%20to%20see%20how%20it%20stacks%20up%20against%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-wet-dry-vacuums%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20wet-dry%20vacuums%3C%2Fa%3E%20out%20there%20today%2C%20so%20I%20put%20it%20to%20work%20in%20my%20multi-pet%20household%20for%20a%20few%20weeks.%20Here's%20everything%20I%20liked%20about%20its%20design%20%E2%80%94%20as%20well%20as%20the%20features%20that%20I'm%20not%20sold%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a9ed8720-2bc5-47eb-a96b-12f238a9bfa2%5C%22%3E%C2%A0Setup%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22All%20the%20pieces%20of%20the%20Shark%20HydroVac%20Pro%20XL%20Cordless%20mop%20before%20being%20assembled.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b349a7a3c8094d5dcff86%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20HydroVac%20has%20a%20lightweight%20cordless%20design%20and%20a%20convenient%20docking%20station.%3Cp%3ECamryn%20Rabideau%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Shark%20HydroVac%20arrived%20on%20my%20doorstep%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20at%20the%20relatively%20small%20size%20of%20the%20package.%20Inside%20the%20box%2C%20there%20were%20only%20a%20few%20pieces%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20unpackaged.%20The%20body%20and%20floorhead%20of%20the%20mop%20were%20one%20connected%20piece%2C%20so%20all%20I%20had%20to%20do%20to%20put%20the%20machine%20together%20was%20insert%20the%20handle.%20I%20also%20removed%20a%20few%20of%20the%20decorative%20stickers%20on%20the%20mop%2C%20but%20I%20left%20some%20of%20the%20ones%20that%20included%20instructions%20for%20its%20operation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20unit's%20base%20was%20also%20inside%20the%20box%2C%20wrapped%20up%20in%20a%20layer%20of%20cardboard%2C%20and%20once%20it%20was%20plugged%20in%2C%20I%20docked%20the%20mop%20by%20placing%20it%20on%20the%20charging%20port.%20It%20took%20around%20four%20hours%20for%20the%20mop%20to%20charge%20up%20completely%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20a%20light%20on%20the%20body%20that%20indicates%20how%20much%20it's%20charged%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20it%20was%20ready%20to%20use.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20jumping%20into%20cleaning%2C%20I%20filled%20up%20the%20machine's%20clean%20water%20tank.%20I%20did%20try%20to%20see%20if%20you%20can%20use%20it%20without%20water%2C%20like%20a%20regular%20vacuum%2C%20but%20the%20mop%20shut%20itself%20off%20and%20flashed%20the%20%26quot%3Bfill%20water%20tank%26quot%3B%20light%20at%20me.%20The%20water%20tank%20is%20easy%20to%20remove%20from%20the%20top%20of%20the%20mop%2C%20and%20it%20has%20lines%20that%20show%20how%20much%20water%20and%20cleaning%20solution%20to%20put%20in.%20However%2C%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20tank%20is%20slanted%2C%20so%20you%20can't%20set%20it%20down%20while%20filling.%20This%20makes%20it%20a%20little%20trickier%20to%20fill%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20too%20bad%20since%20the%20tank%20is%20quite%20small.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d5be9325-acee-4e7b-90a4-e2cc628fd93a%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Our%20review%20of%20the%20Shark%20HydroVac%20Pro%20XL%20vacuum%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20review%20of%20the%20Shark%20HydroVac%20Pro%20XL%20vacuum%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Shark%20HydroVac%20Pro%20XL%20Cordless%20mop%20docked%20on%20its%20base.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b2e8950edbc52a8643a09%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20HydroVac%20has%20an%20antimicrobial%20brushroll%20that%20scrubs%20your%20floors%2C%20removing%20spills%20and%20stains.%3Cp%3ECamryn%20Rabideau%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELiving%20on%20a%20busy%20homestead%2C%20I%20typically%20break%20out%20my%20mop%20at%20least%20two%20or%20three%20times%20a%20week%2C%20typically%20to%20clean%20up%20pet%20messes%2C%20dirt%20that's%20been%20tracked%20into%20the%20house%2C%20or%20eggs%20that%20roll%20off%20the%20counter%20when%20cooking.%20I%20love%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20mop%20that%20does%20all%20the%20work%20for%20me%20%E2%80%94%20usually%20I%20have%20to%20put%20my%20back%20into%20it%20when%20scrubbing%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20happily%20used%20the%20Shark%20HydroVac%20Pro%20XL%20as%20part%20of%20my%20everyday%20cleaning%20routine%20for%20several%20weeks.%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2216c63d5e-0da3-466b-b31c-71b143fc52e1%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Ease%20of%20use%5C%22%3EEase%20of%20use%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Shark%20HydroVac%20only%20weighs%20around%208%20pounds%20%E2%80%94%20roughly%20the%20same%20weight%20as%20a%20cordless%20vacuum%20%E2%80%94%20though%20it%20is%20quite%20bottom-heavy.%20Still%2C%20it's%20light%20enough%20to%20carry%20from%20room%20to%20room%2C%20and%20it's%20easy%20to%20maneuver%20around%20the%20floor%20while%20mopping.%20It%20rolls%20smoothly%20on%20the%20forward%20stroke%2C%20but%20there's%20a%20bit%20more%20resistance%20when%20you%20pull%20it%20backward.%20I%20also%20found%20that%20its%20swivel%20steering%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20navigate%20around%20obstacles%2C%20and%20I%20could%20even%20clean%20under%20the%20edge%20of%20my%20kitchen%20counter%20by%20tilting%20the%20body%20of%20the%20mop%20to%20the%20side.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20HydroVac's%20control%20buttons%2C%20which%20allow%20you%20to%20turn%20it%20on%2Foff%20and%20change%20the%20mode%2C%20are%20right%20on%20the%20handle.%20I%20accidentally%20hit%20the%20mode%20button%20a%20few%20times%20when%20I%20first%20used%20the%20mop%2C%20as%20I%20was%20holding%20the%20handle%20up%20too%20far.%20There%20are%20also%20two%20small%20headlights%20on%20either%20side%20of%20the%20mop's%20brushroll%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20find%20them%20to%20be%20useful%20%E2%80%94%20they%20only%20light%20up%20a%20small%20area%2C%20and%20the%20light%20isn't%20powerful%20enough%20to%20actually%20illuminate%20any%20dirt.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20only%20major%20complaint%20about%20the%20HydroVac's%20design%20is%20that%20it%20sometimes%20drips%20dirty%20water%20when%20you%20stand%20it%20upright.%20For%20instance%2C%20when%20I%20was%20mopping%20my%20kitchen%2C%20I%20stopped%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20floor%20mat%20in%20front%20of%20the%20sink%2C%20turning%20the%20mop%20off%20and%20standing%20it%20up.%20When%20I%20was%20ready%20to%20resume%20cleaning%2C%20there%20was%20a%20small%20puddle%20underneath%20the%20machine.%20I%20was%20able%20to%20just%20go%20over%20the%20liquid%20again%20when%20I%20turned%20the%20HydroVac%20back%20on%2C%20but%20I%20also%20ran%20into%20this%20issue%20if%20I%20didn't%20immediately%20dock%20the%20unit%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20cleaning%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20small%20puddle%20of%20dirty%20water%20next%20to%20the%20base%20of%20the%20Shark%20HydroVac%20mop.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b34fd50edbc52a8643fa8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20mop%20occasionally%20left%20behind%20small%20puddles%20of%20dirty%20water%20when%20left%20upright.%3Cp%3ECamryn%20Rabideau%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c5ca9a71-8129-460e-a240-e65036449bd9%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cleaning%20performance%5C%22%3ECleaning%20performance%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20the%20HydroVac%20does%20a%20good%20job%20getting%20dirt%2C%20grime%2C%20and%20spills%20off%20any%20type%20of%20hard%20flooring.%20The%20brushroll%2C%20which%20the%20brand%20claims%20has%20an%20antimicrobial%20finish%2C%20spins%20quickly%20to%20create%20a%20strong%20scrubbing%20action%2C%20and%20it%20was%20perfect%20for%20cleaning%20up%20dirt%20and%20scuffs%20in%20my%20entryway%2C%20water%20marks%20around%20my%20dog's%20water%20bowl%2C%20and%20small%20everyday%20messes%2C%20like%20dirty%20footprints%20that%20were%20tracked%20into%20the%20house.%20I%20was%20also%20impressed%20by%20the%20mop's%20ability%20to%20pick%20up%20pet%20hair%20as%20I%20cleaned.%20It%20was%20able%20to%20pick%20up%20small%20clumps%20of%20hair%20around%20the%20edges%20of%20the%20room%2C%20saving%20me%20the%20hassle%20of%20vacuuming%20before%20mopping.%20The%20HydroVac%20was%20also%20able%20to%20pick%20up%20small%20debris%20like%20cat%20litter%2C%20spilled%20coffee%20grounds%20and%20pieces%20of%20grass%20that%20got%20tracked%20inside%2C%20and%20it%20even%20handled%20larger%20pieces%20of%20debris%20like%20Cheerios%20in%20just%20a%20few%20passes.%20(It%20did%20break%20up%20a%20few%20of%20them%2C%20but%20was%20able%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20crumbs%20on%20the%20next%20pass.)%20The%20mop%20does%20leave%20behind%20a%20visible%20trail%20of%20moisture%2C%20which%20lets%20you%20keep%20track%20of%20where%20you've%20cleaned%2C%20but%20it%20dries%20within%20a%20few%20minutes%20and%20doesn't%20leave%20any%20steaks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20using%20the%20mop%20for%20everyday%20cleaning%20needs%2C%20I%20also%20set%20up%20a%20series%20of%20obstacles%20to%20test%20its%20abilities.%20I%20spilled%20generous%20amounts%20of%20maple%20syrup%2C%20soda%2C%20ketchup%2C%20and%20dirt%20onto%20the%20floor%20and%20let%20them%20dry%20for%20several%20hours.%20I%20used%20the%20HydroVac%20to%20clean%20up%20each%20spill%2C%20seeing%20how%20many%20passes%20it%20took%20to%20completely%20get%20rid%20of%20the%20mark%20and%20any%20residue.%20It%20made%20quick%20work%20of%20the%20dirt%20and%20soda%2C%20leaving%20the%20floor%20clean%20in%20just%20two%20passes.%20The%20ketchup%20required%20a%20few%20extra%20strokes%20to%20break%20up%20the%20dried-on%20residue%2C%20and%20the%20maple%20syrup%20needed%20several%20passes%20before%20all%20the%20sticky%20residue%20was%20gone.%20So%20as%20long%20as%20you%20have%20patience%2C%20the%20HydroVac%20should%20be%20able%20to%20tackle%20virtually%20any%20spill%2C%20even%20if%20it's%20dried%20and%20crusty.%20I%20also%20appreciated%20that%20the%20fresh%20water%20tank%20holds%20enough%20water%20to%20get%20through%20an%20entire%20cleaning%20cycle%20%E2%80%94%20it%20had%20just%20a%20small%20amount%20of%20water%20left%20at%20the%20end%20of%20its%20battery%20life%2C%20which%20saved%20me%20from%20having%20to%20stop%20and%20refill%20mid-clean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Shark%20HydroVac%20Pro%20XL%20Cordless%20mop%20cleaning%20up%20ketchup%20on%20hardwood%20floors.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b35a750edbc52a8644013%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20HydroVac%20was%20able%20to%20clean%20up%20ketchup%20and%20other%20spills%20in%20just%20a%20few%20passes.%3Cp%3ECamryn%20Rabideau%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20HydroVac%20also%20has%20a%20special%20mode%20for%20cleaning%20area%20rugs%2C%20and%20while%20I%20tried%20it%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20this%20review%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20I'll%20be%20using%20it%20again.%20The%20brand%20claims%20this%20mode%20%26quot%3Bremoves%20surface%20dirt%20and%20odors%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20it%20really%20didn't%20seem%20to%20do%20much%20to%20the%20rug%20in%20my%20dining%20room.%20When%20you%20put%20the%20mop%20on%20%26quot%3BRug%20mode%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20seems%20like%20it%20uses%20less%20water%2C%20but%20there%20aren't%20any%20bristles%20on%20the%20roller%2C%20it%20doesn't%20do%20anything%20to%20loosen%20dirt%20and%20dust%20from%20the%20rug.%20It%20basically%20just%20skims%20over%20the%20surface%20%E2%80%94%20the%20rug%20felt%20damp%2C%20but%20there%20was%20still%20visible%20dirt%20and%20debris%20that%20the%20mop%20didn't%20pick%20up.%20It%20was%20able%20to%20pick%20up%20a%20handful%20of%20Cheerios%20in%20around%20four%20passes%2C%20but%20it%20left%20the%20rug%20quite%20wet%20in%20the%20process.%20I%20didn't%20notice%20any%20odor-neutralizing%20effects%2C%20but%20my%20rug%20also%20didn't%20smell%20strongly%20to%20begin%20with.%20Overall%2C%20it's%20adequate%20if%20you're%20already%20mopping%20and%20want%20to%20give%20your%20rug%20a%20quick%20touch-up%2C%20but%20it's%20definitely%20not%20a%20replacement%20for%20a%20full-size%20vacuum%20or%20carpet%20cleaner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22446caff4-852e-4a54-bf85-791b0b8739b6%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Battery%20life%5C%22%3EBattery%20life%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20mention%20of%20battery%20life%20within%20the%20HydroVac's%20product%20listing%2C%20so%20I%20really%20didn't%20know%20what%20to%20expect%20from%20the%20mop%2C%20though%20Shark%20confirmed%20with%20us%20the%20battery%20runtime%20is%20about%2020%20minutes.%20To%20find%20out%20how%20long%20it%20would%20run%2C%20I%20waited%20until%20the%20unit%20was%20fully%20charged%2C%20then%20started%20a%20timer%20on%20my%20phone%20and%20started%20cleaning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20able%20to%20mop%20for%2016%20minutes%20continuously%20before%20the%20battery%20indicator%20light%20started%20flashing%2C%20indicating%20that%20it%20was%20nearly%20empty.%20I%20opted%20to%20stop%20then%20to%20make%20sure%20I%20had%20enough%20battery%20life%20to%20run%20the%20self-cleaning%20cycle%2C%20but%20I%20imagine%20you%20could%20make%20it%20a%20few%20more%20minutes%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20to%2018%20or%2020%20minutes%20%E2%80%94%20before%20the%20mop%20completely%20died.%20In%20the%2016%20minutes%20of%20use%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20mop%20my%20entire%20kitchen%2C%20going%20over%20the%20floor%20twice%20for%20a%20thorough%20clean%2C%20as%20well%20as%20my%20entryway%20and%20most%20of%20my%20living%20room.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226fedfbea-b508-4b3e-a04c-6914c5b35482%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Maintenance%5C%22%3EMaintenance%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EHands%20down%2C%20the%20worst%20part%20about%20using%20the%20HydroVac%20is%20cleaning%20it.%20When%20you%20finish%20mopping%2C%20you%20have%20to%20empty%20the%20dirty%20water%20tank%20before%20you%20run%20the%20machine's%20self-cleaning%20cycle%2C%20so%20I%20took%20the%20tank%20off%20the%20machine%20and%20brought%20it%20to%20the%20bathroom.%20It%20dripped%20gross%20brown%20water%20out%20the%20bottom%20while%20I%20was%20carrying%20it%2C%20so%20I'd%20recommend%20taking%20the%20tank%20off%20relatively%20close%20to%20your%20sink%20and%20not%20bringing%20it%20across%20the%20whole%20house%20like%20I%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dirty%20water%20being%20poured%20out%20of%20the%20Shark%20HydroVac%E2%80%99s%20dirty%20water%20tank.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b35ff0ec98e92f74f7bd5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20can%20easily%20pour%20dirty%20liquid%20out%20of%20the%20water%20tank%2C%20but%20it's%20harder%20to%20remove%20the%20solid%20debris.%3Cp%3ECamryn%20Rabideau%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20instructions%20on%20the%20back%20of%20the%20tank%20that%20tell%20you%20the%20proper%20way%20to%20empty%20it%2C%20and%20the%20first%20step%20is%20to%20pour%20the%20dirty%20liquid%20out%20the%20spout.%20Easy.%20Then%20comes%20the%20gross%20part%20%E2%80%94%20emptying%20the%20%26quot%3Bsolid%26quot%3B%20debris%2C%20which%20in%20my%20case%2C%20was%20a%20mixture%20of%20dog%20hair%2C%20dirt%2C%20and%20other%20gunk.%20There%20was%20a%20large%20clump%20of%20debris%20every%20time%20I%20used%20the%20vacuum%2C%20and%20it%20needed%20to%20be%20pushed%20out%20of%20the%20little%20compartment.%20It%20reminded%20me%20of%20the%20slimy%20gunk%20that%20you%20pull%20out%20of%20a%20shower%20drain%20(gag!)%2C%20and%20I%20really%2C%20%3Cem%3Ereally%3C%2Fem%3E%20wish%20the%20brand%20included%20a%20tool%20for%20this%20part%20of%20the%20cleaning%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20debris%20was%20removed%2C%20I%20rinsed%20off%20all%20the%20pieces%20and%20reassembled%20them.%20I%20generally%20had%20to%20fill%20up%20the%20machine's%20clean%20water%20tank%20before%20running%20the%20self-clean%20cycle%2C%20as%20the%20manual%20says%20you%20need%20at%20least%20half%20a%20tank.%20To%20self-clean%20the%20mop%2C%20you%20just%20place%20it%20on%20its%20base%20and%20press%20power.%20It%20runs%20the%20brushroll%20with%20fresh%20water%20for%20around%20two%20minutes%20to%20clean%20off%20all%20the%20lingering%20dirt.%20I%20also%20noticed%20there%20was%20dog%20hair%20stuck%20under%20the%20brushroll%20cover%2C%20so%20I%20had%20to%20remove%20it%20and%20clean%20that%20off%2C%20too.%20Once%20the%20brushroll%20dried%20after%20self-cleaning%2C%20it%20looked%20as%20good%20as%20new%2C%20and%20there%20weren't%20any%20lingering%20odors%20%E2%80%94%20I%20was%20definitely%20impressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20waste%20bin%20of%20the%20Shark%20HydroVac%20filled%20with%20pet%20hair%20and%20debris.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b36ca0ec98e92f74f7c3f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20mop%20captures%20solid%20debris%20in%20a%20removable%20compartment%2C%20but%20it's%20tricky%20to%20empty.%3Cp%3ECamryn%20Rabideau%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBottom%20line%3F%20If%20you're%20squeamish%2C%20you're%20definitely%20going%20to%20be%20grossed%20out%20while%20cleaning%20the%20HydroVac.%20I%20can%20appreciate%20that%20the%20dirty%20liquid%20and%20solid%20debris%20are%20separated%2C%20but%20the%20slimy%2C%20wet%20ball%20of%20pet%20hair%20is%20still%20gross%20to%20touch.%20There's%20really%20no%20easy%20way%20to%20get%20the%20debris%20out%20without%20touching%20it%2C%20either%20%E2%80%94%20I%20usually%20ended%20up%20pulling%20it%20out%20with%20a%20paper%20towel.%20I%20suppose%20you%20could%20try%20banging%20it%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20a%20trash%20can%2C%20but%20I'd%20be%20worried%20it%20would%20leave%20dirty%20splatter%20marks%20everywhere.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2210aaa5b9-9877-4e3c-92a2-5b1edc3ffb9a%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20downside%20of%20the%20Shark%20HydroVac%20Pro%20XL%20Cordless%20is%20definitely%20the%20process%20of%20cleaning%20out%20its%20dirty%20water%20tank.%20The%20liquid%20is%20easy%20enough%20to%20pour%20down%20the%20drain%2C%20but%20you%20have%20to%20pull%20out%20solid%20debris%20by%20hand.%20If%20you%20have%20pets%2C%20this%20means%20touching%20a%20wet%20clump%20of%20grimy%20dog%20hair%20%E2%80%94%20yuck!%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20if%20you're%20hoping%20to%20use%20the%20HydroVac%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-carpet-cleaner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20carpet%20cleaners%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you'll%20likely%20be%20disappointed%20in%20its%20performance.%20The%20mop%20does%20have%20a%20special%20mode%20for%20cleaning%20area%20rugs%2C%20but%20it%20left%20visible%20dirt%20and%20pet%20hair%20behind%20and%20didn't%20seem%20to%20do%20much%20besides%20leave%20the%20carpet%20feeling%20damp.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c242ac65-c27e-49f2-998b-da96c65f8dc2%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20are%20your%20alternatives