re%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20a%20serial%20plant%20killer%20like%20I%20am%2C%20you're%20probably%20familiar%20with%20the%20struggle.%20My%20most%20recent%20plant%20victim%20was%20a%20Venus%20Flytrap%2C%20lovingly%20named%20Frederick%2C%20which%20I%20somehow%20killed%20despite%20my%20promises%20that%20this%20time%20I'd%20keep%20it%20alive.%20I%20gave%20it%20distilled%20water%2C%20repotted%20it%20in%20specialty%20soil%2C%20and%20placed%20it%20near%20my%20sunny-but-not-too-sunny%20window.%20Despite%20my%20best%20efforts%2C%20Frederick%20tragically%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I've%20now%20shifted%20the%20strategy%20entirely%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fgifts%2Fwhere-to-buy-plants-online%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elive%20plants%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20added%20greenery%20to%20my%20home%20using%20something%20untraditional%3A%20Lego%20flowers%20and%20plants.%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Dcbc9d75c99539612a7a47b029258371e5091fafd091b48baa3defdf8c8650c5b%26postID%3D684062c46a874b0bc939d91f%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Flego-botanical-collection-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.lego.com%252Fen-us%252Fthemes%252Fadults-welcome%252Fbotanical-collection%252Fartificial-flowers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Lego%20Botanical%20Collection%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20a%20variety%20of%20flora%2C%20from%20orchids%20to%20succulents%2C%20all%20made%20from%20Lego%20bricks%20and%20studs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20building%20eight%20sets%20and%20counting%20from%20the%20Botanical%20Collection%20since%20its%20launch%20four%20years%20ago%2C%20Lego%20plants%20and%20flowers%20are%20my%20favorite%20home%20decor%20hack.%20They%20make%20great%20gifts%2C%20too.%20Plus%2C%20even%20after%20all%20this%20time%2C%20they're%20still%20looking%20as%20green%20as%20ever%2C%20which%20I%20can't%20say%20about%20my%20other%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226c8f52fd-39b7-4834-a4e1-d9aef6b297bc%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22A%20few%20of%20our%20favorites%5C%22%3EA%20few%20of%20our%20favorites%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222e0870be-1e93-42a4-b4f3-1d497c6db504%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Our%20review%20of%20the%20Lego%20Botanicals%20Collection%5C%22%3EOur%20review%20of%20the%20Lego%20Botanicals%20Collection%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Lego%20sunflowers%20set%2C%20including%20the%20box%2C%20instructions%2C%20and%20bagged%20pieces.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684077adc19ab3675c10a1f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20sunflowers%20are%20one%20of%20the%20cheaper%20sets.%20You%20can%20snag%20two%20sunflower%20stems%20for%20%2415.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a40e9a9c-bcb8-4624-ac44-db45229af16f%5C%22%3EStep-by-step%20instructions%20make%20assembly%20easy%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20you're%20a%20Lego%20veteran%20or%20newcomer%2C%20building%20Lego%20plants%20and%20flowers%20is%20fun%20and%20easy.%20I%20think%20the%20process%20is%20simple%20and%20easy%20to%20follow.%20Each%20set%20comes%20with%20a%20full-color%2C%20illustrated%20booklet%20with%20step-by-step%20instructions%20on%20how%20to%20build%20your%20plants%20or%20flowers.%20The%20set%20is%20divided%20into%20bags%2C%20so%20it's%20easy%20to%20find%20the%20pieces%20you%20need.%20If%20you%20prefer%20a%20high-tech%20option%2C%20there's%20also%20a%20Lego%20app%20with%20instructions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESets%20take%20anywhere%20between%2030%20minutes%20to%20two%20hours%20to%20build%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20set%20and%20your%20building%20efficiency.%20I%20love%20putting%20on%20some%20music%2C%20setting%20out%20the%20instructions%2C%20and%20building%20to%20my%20heart's%20content.%20It's%20a%20great%20way%20to%20get%20away%20from%20screens%20for%20a%20bit%2C%20and%20it's%20so%20satisfying%20to%20see%20your%20set%20come%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lego%20sunflowers%20mid-build%2C%20with%20the%20instructions%20and%20leaf%20and%20stem%20pieces%20sitting%20to%20the%20side.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6840785d9b2a601d01b24b9d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20sunflower%20petals%20are%20made%20from%20yellow%20oar%20pieces%2C%20which%20is%20just%20one%20example%20of%20the%20innovative%20designs%20in%20the%20Lego%20Botanicals%20Collection.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225f59293f-d438-4898-9325-ea5da18e3700%5C%22%3EThe%20sets%20are%20customizable%2C%20and%20mixing%20and%20matching%20is%20encouraged%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20my%20favorite%20parts%20of%20the%20Botanicals%20Collection%20is%20its%20customization.%20The%20flower%20sets%20all%20come%20with%20adjustable%20stems%2C%20so%20you%20can%20change%20the%20height%20of%20your%20flowers%20for%20your%20ideal%20look%20or%20vase%20height.%20Other%20sets%20have%20different%20customization%20options%2C%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D1c31b38590c6c0c2849c38c301a582117988fec0d44ed3ce1dfaa47993ed629e%26postID%3D684062c46a874b0bc939d91f%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Flego-botanical-collection-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FLEGO-Building-Project-Beautiful-Display%252Fdp%252FB08HVXZW8X%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBonsai%20Tree%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20you%20can%20choose%20between%20green%20foliage%20or%20pink%20cherry%20blossoms.%20I%20chose%20the%20pink%20cherry%20blossoms.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D3d8e0d3fefb8f61281d7d6d2e8115bd8ff0b11a1b07b8049ae6ff6f98fdbc12a%26postID%3D684062c46a874b0