jects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20trend%20I%20told%20you%20about%20back%20in%20April.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-apple-building-blocks-chatgpt-data-centers-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egenerative%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20boom%20is%20pushing%20companies%20to%20adopt%20different%20pricing%20models%2C%20partly%20because%20the%20latest%20models%20have%20become%20so%20expensive%20to%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsaas-ai-changing-how-software-companies-charge-customers-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etaking%20hold%20in%20the%20SaaS%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Now%20it%20is%20beginning%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconsulting-ai-mckinsey-bcg-deloitte-pwc-kpmg-chatbots-ai-tools-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehappen%20in%20consulting.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGlobant%2C%20an%20IT%20services%20specialist%20that%20competes%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faccenture-doge-hitting-business-financial-results-ceo-julie-sweet-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAccenture%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20other%20consulting%20firms%2C%20is%20rolling%20out%20AI%20Pods%2C%20a%20subscription%20for%20AI-powered%20offerings%20including%20software%20engineering%2C%20product%20definition%2C%20design%2C%20and%20testing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClients%20can%20subscribe%20monthly%20to%20an%20AI%20Pod%2C%20and%20each%20subscription%20includes%20token-based%20capacity%2C%20similar%20to%20how%20some%20leading%20AI%20labs%20structure%20usage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20time%20a%20company%20taps%20into%20a%20major%20AI%20model%2C%20the%20prompts%20and%20other%20requests%20are%20broken%20down%20into%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-jensen-huang-ai-factory-tokens-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etokens%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20new%20language%20of%20generative%20AI%2C%20which%20have%20to%20be%20processed.%20When%20complex%20projects%20are%20handled%20this%20way%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20token%20processing%20can%20add%20up%20quickly%2C%20especially%20if%20newer%2C%20%26quot%3Breasoning%26quot%3B%20models%20are%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETraditional%20consulting%20projects%20often%20come%20with%20time-intensive%20billing%20structures%3A%20work%20is%20scoped%2C%20employees%20are%20assigned%2C%20and%20hours%20are%20tracked%20to%20calculate%20what%20to%20charge%20clients.%20But%20in%20the%20world%20of%20generative%20AI%2C%20where%20outputs%20are%20driven%20by%20token-based%20usage%20and%20cost%20varies%20depending%20on%20the%20models%20used%2C%20the%20old%20approach%20could%20create%20misalignment%20between%20providers%20and%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20departure%20from%20the%20traditional%20effort-based%20approaches%2C%26quot%3B%20Globant%20CEO%20Mart%C3%ADn%20Migoya%20explained%2C%20describing%20the%20move%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bradical%20departure%20from%20what%20anyone%20else%20in%20our%20industry%20is%20offering.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226f484b49-37df-4888-84a8-2bb755b75f0b%5C%22%3ETokens%20versus%20effort%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGlobant's%20new%20AI%20Pods%20package%20this%20new%20reality%20into%20a%20managed-services%20model%3A%20for%20a%20monthly%20subscription%20fee%2C%20clients%20access%20a%20virtual%20workforce%20of%20AI%20agents%20supervised%20by%20Globant's%20human%20tech%20consultants.%20Each%20subscription%20comes%20with%20a%20certain%20number%20of%20tokens%20to%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20only%20a%20theoretical%20example%20and%20doesn't%20represent%20what%20Globant%20will%20actually%20charge%20clients%2C%20but%20you%20get%20the%20gist%3A%20A%20client%20might%20pay%20%2420%2C000%20a%20month%20and%20get%20100%20million%20tokens%20included%20in%20that%20subscription.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20business%20is%20to%20create%20software%20for%20you%2C%20to%20create%20technology%20for%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Migoya%20added%20in%20an%20interview.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20proposing%20a%20novel%20way%20of%20engaging%2C%20which%20is%20more%20connected%20to%20throughput%20rather%20than%20just%20the%20time%20and%20effort%20I'm%20consuming.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMigoya%20said%20the%20token%20limits%20are%20high%2C%20so%20Globant%20consultants%20and%20their%20clients%20have%20more%20than%20enough%20to%20get%20projects%20completed.%20If%20some%20customers%20blow%20through%20token%20allocations%2C%20Globant%20will%20work%20out%20solutions%2C%20but%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20keep%20pricing%20stable%20in%20this%20new%20generative%20AI%20era%2C%20while%20minimizing%20surprises%2C%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22245a59c4-6f05-453f-be86-197893259eab%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BStreaming%26quot%3B%20consulting%20services%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Bstreaming%20engineering%2C%26quot%3B%20likening%20it%20to%20how%20we%20pay%20a%20monthly%20fee%20to%20stream%20Netflix%20movies%20and%20TV%20shows.%20Instead%20of%20spinning%20up%20custom%20teams%20for%20every%20client%20need%2C%20customers%20now%20subscribe%20to%20digital%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20hood%2C%20the%20AI%20Pods%20are%20powered%20by%20Globant%20Enterprise%20AI%20platform%2C%20which%20taps%20into%20different%20leading%20AI%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20also%20uses%20its%20own%20agent%20framework%2C%20CODA%2C%20which%20automates%20aspects%20of%20code%20generation%2C%20testing%2C%20and%20deployment%20while%20ensuring%20high-quality%20enterprise%20output.%20This%20approach%20lets%20Globant%20reuse%20existing%20software%20components%2C%20which%20reduces%20the%20need%20to%20ping%20the%20underlying%20AI%20models%20(reducing%20those%20token-processing%20costs!).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGlobant%20says%20the%20new%20model%20is%20already%20being%20used%20by%20clients%20in%20finance%2C%20entertainment%2C%20and%20energy.%20Early%20adopters%20include%20oil%20and%20gas%20company%20YPF%20and%20holding%20company%20JM%20Family%20Enterprises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20subscription-based%20and%20token-based%20models%20have%20caught%20on%20in%20the%20SaaS%20world%2C%20Globant's%20move%20is%20a%20signal%20that%20enterprise%20consulting%20may%20be%20heading%20the%20same%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeloitte-ey-launch-agentic-ai-platforms-big-four-competition2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elargest%20consulting%20firms%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20including%20Deloitte%2C%20EY%2C%20PwC%2C%20and%20KPMG%2C%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkpmg-ai-boss-david-rowlands-artificial-intelligence-strategy-big-four-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Einvesting%20heavily%20in%20automation%20and%20AI%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3Eover%20the%20past%20few%20years.%20Recently%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeloitte-accenture-job-fears-doge-consulting-contracts-trump-musk-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EDeloitte%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20EY%20announced%20new%20agentic%20AI%20platforms%2C%20both%20built%20in%20collaboration%20with%20Nvidia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20AI%20redefining%20how%20software%20is%20built%20and%20deployed%2C%20billing%20just%20based%20on%20human%20time%20and%20effort%20may%20soon%20feel%20as%20outdated%20as%20dial-up%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconsulting-firm-rips-up-traditional-billing-playbook-ai-era-globant-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749124802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6840d535c19ab3675c10ac99%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconsulting-firm-rips-up-traditional-billing-playbook-ai-era-globant-2025-6%22%2