uring%20efforts.%20Companies%20are%20prioritizing%20profitability%20and%20streamlining%20operations%2C%20leading%20to%20workforce%20reductions%20across%20various%20divisions%20and%20management%20levels.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Flayoffs-in-2025-google-microsoft-intel-in-284-technology-companies-that-cut-jobs-in-first-5-months-of-the-year%2Farticleshow%2F121646617.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20A%20City%20Running%20Out%20of%20Green%2C%20This%20Vast%20Vikhroli%20Mangrove%20Has%20Protected%20Mumbai%20for%204%20Decades%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20sponsored%20by%20Godrej%20Enterprises%20Group%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%E2%80%99ve%20ever%20driven%20from%20Mumbai%20towards%20Thane%20on%20the%20Eastern%20Express%20Highway%2C%20you%20might%20have%20felt%20a%20gradual%20dip%20in%20temperature%20of%20up%20to%20five%20degrees.%20As%20you%20pass%20Ghatkopar%20and%20approach%20Kanjurmarg%2C%20your%20windows%20fog%20up%20slightly%2C%20the%20air%20cools%2C%20and%20everything%20seems%20a%20little%20quieter.%20No%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20your%20imagination%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20mangroves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20your%20right%2C%20hidden%20behind%20the%20industrial%20facade%20of%20the%20city%2C%20lies%20one%20of%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20best-kept%20secrets%3A%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F414695%2Fgorai-mangrove-park-in-mumbai-opening%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esprawling%20mangrove%20forest%3C%2Fa%3E%20quietly%20flourishing%20within%20the%20Godrej%20Enterprises%20Group%E2%80%99s%20Pirojshanagar%20Township%20in%20Vikhroli.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpread%20over%20thousands%20of%20acres%2C%20this%20green%20lung%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20offering%20a%20coo