0consultation%20with%20none%20other%20than%20Dr%20Salim%20Ali%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20respected%20ornithologist%2C%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20the%20conservation%20strategy%20that%20followed.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20didn%E2%80%99t%20just%20fence%20the%20forest%20and%20call%20it%20preservation.%20The%20early%20work%20involved%20a%20four-year%20baseline%20study%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20first%20doctorate-level%20research%20projects%20on%20mangrove%20conservation%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Tejashree%20Joshi%2C%20Head%20of%20Environmental%20Sustainability%20at%20Godrej%20Enterprises%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20research%20uncovered%20not%20just%20which%20species%20lived%20here%2C%20but%20how%20they%20survived%2C%20coexisted%20or%20were%20at%20risk..%20%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20time%20when%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98mangrove%E2%80%99%20was%20confused%20with%20%E2%80%98mango%E2%80%99%2C%20this%20research%20provided%20the%20foundation%20and%20a%20science-backed%20roadmap%3A%20what%20to%20protect%2C%20where%20to%20intervene%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20why%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20an%20expert%20from%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20science%20rooted%20the%20forest%E2%80%99s%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmed%20with%20data%20and%20information%2C%20the%20Godrej%20team%20rolled%20out%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F331813%2Fkochi-murukesan-plants-lakhs-of-mangrove-along-kerala-coastline-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethree-pronged%20conservation%3C%2Fa%3E%20model%20that%20still%20guides%20the%20initiative%20today%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EResearch%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Baseline%20biodiversity%20studies%2C%20continuous%20ecological%20monitoring%2C%20species%20inventory%20updates.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EConservation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Securing%20the%20forest%2C%20replanting%20native%20mangroves%2C%20controlling%20access%2C%20and%20preventing%20exploitation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECreating%20awareness%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Educating%20employees%2C%20local%20communities%2C%20and%20schoolchildren%20through%20immersive%2C%20long-term%20engagement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20about%20ticking%20the%20Environmental%2C%20Social%2C%20and%20Governance%20(ESG)%20boxes%20%E2%80%94%20the%20work%20began%20decades%20before%20the%20term%20or%20even%20laws%20even%20existed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20initiative%20is%20not%20part%20of%20our%20CSR.%20It%E2%80%99s%20funded%20internally%20and%20has%20been%20since%20day%20one.%20That%20matters%2C%20because%20it%20reflects%20genuine%20belief%20rather%20than%20compliance%2C%E2%80%9D%20Joshi%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20mangroves%20matter%20now%20more%20than%20ever%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMangroves%20are%20often%20called%20the%20guardians%20of%20the%20coast%2C%20and%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20more%20truth%20than%20metaphor.%20These%20salt-tolerant%20forests%20act%20as%20natural%20infrastructure%2C%20quietly%20protecting%20the%20city%20from%20climate%20shocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMangroves%20trap%20carbon%20dioxide%2C%20provide%20oxygen%2C%20protect%20against%20erosion%2C%20and%20serve%20as%20nurseries%20for%20aquatic%20life.%20In%20a%20coastal%20city%20like%20Mumbai%2C%20their%20value%20cannot%20be%20overstated%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Dr.%20Ninad%2C%20the%20expert.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Natural%20climate%20defence%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20intensifying%20monsoons%20and%20rising%20sea%20levels%2C%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20flood%20risk%20grows%20each%20year.%20Mangroves%20act%20like%20sponges%2C%20absorbing%20excess%20rainwater%20and%20buffering%20coastlines%20from%20storm%20surges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20we%E2