l%20hub%20of%20the%20world.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStefan%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20lot%20of%20China%E2%80%99s%20chemical%20industry%20is%20coal-based.%20India%20has%20the%20biomass%20and%20a%20chance%20to%20leapfrog.%20If%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20reduce%20our%20environmental%20footprint%2C%20we%20won%E2%80%99t%20survive.%20Nature%20will%20carry%20on%20%E2%80%94%20but%20we%20won%E2%80%99t.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20pauses.%20%E2%80%9CDid%20you%20know%20that%20if%20the%20South%20Pole%20melts%20completely%2C%20the%20sea%20level%20could%20rise%20by%2060%20metres%3F%20That%20would%20wipe%20out%20most%20of%20the%20Earth%E2%80%99s%20fertile%20land.%E2%80%9D%20It%E2%80%99s%20this%20urgency%20and%20opportunity%20that%20drives%20BCML%E2%80%99s%20mission.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20help%20make%20this%20bio-revolution%20happen%E2%80%A6%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20excites%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20future%20of%20plastics%20via%20Balrampur%20Bioyug%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20Avantika%20envisions%20a%20future%20where%20BCML%20harnesses%20the%20full%20potential%20of%20PLA%20once%20the%20plant%20starts%20functioning%20by%20the%20end%20of%202026.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20five%20years%2C%20I%20want%20to%20maximise%20the%20potential%20of%20PLA.%20Of%20course%2C%20we%20can%20do%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20while%20the%20ambition%20is%20clear%2C%20it%20will%20require%20collective%20movement%20across%20industry%20and%20government.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20broader%20goal%20includes%20exploring%20other%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F124274%2Fbioplastic-prawn-shells-angelina-arora-sydney-innovation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebiomaterials%20and%20green%20chemicals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20long-term%20value%20addition.%20For%20Avantika%2C%20sustainability%20isn%E2%80