ore%20urgent%20with%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1881761%23%3A~%3Atext%3DProducers%2520of%2520notified%2520EEE%252C%2520have%2Cbeyond%2520the%2520maximum%2520prescribed%2520concentration.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20E-Waste%20(Management)%20Rules%2C%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20now%20in%20place.%20These%20rules%20require%20all%20manufacturers%20of%20electronic%20products%20to%20take%20responsibility%20for%20what%20happens%20to%20their%20products%20after%20use%20%E2%80%94%20a%20principle%20known%20as%20Extended%20Producer%20Responsibility%20(EPR).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20simple%20terms%2C%20companies%20must%20ensure%20their%20e-waste%20is%20being%20collected%2C%20recycled%2C%20and%20disposed%20of%20safely%2C%20not%20just%20tossed%20aside.%20The%20law%20also%20sets%20clear%20targets%3A%20by%202023-24%20and%202024-25%2C%2060%25%20of%20e-waste%20generated%20must%20be%20recycled.%20That%20figure%20rises%20to%2070%25%20in%20the%20following%20two%20years%20and%20hits%2080%25%20from%202027-28%20onwards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHulladek%E2%80%99s%20work%20makes%20it%20possible%20for%20both%20individuals%20and%20industries%20to%20meet%20these%20goals%2C%20not%20just%20on%20paper%2C%20but%20in%20real%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-3-1748957873.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20company%20operates%20with%20a%20dual%20approach%2C%20holding%20collection%20drives%20for%20households%20and%20managing%20e-waste%20for%20major%20corporations.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-3-1748957873.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fu