nt%20industry%2C%20and%20our%20gender%20diversity%20is%20unparalleled%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shreya%20beams%20with%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHulladek%E2%80%99s%20work%20is%20rooted%20in%20an%20apparent%20belief%3A%20change%20begins%20with%20awareness.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20the%20organisation%20has%20built%20a%20formidable%20logistics%20network%20backed%20by%20intention%20and%20community%20engagement.%20With%20more%20than%2060%20collection%20centres%20spread%20across%20cities%20like%20Surat%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Coimbatore%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20Delhi%2C%20and%20Agartala%2C%20Hulladek%20conducts%20over%20500%20awareness%20sessions%20each%20year%E2%80%94each%20one%20an%20attempt%20to%20shift%20mindsets%20and%20turn%20passive%20consumers%20into%20conscious%20participants%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20e-waste%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Eastern%20India%2C%20their%20presence%20is%20especially%20significant.%20In%20cities%20like%20Kolkata%2C%20Hulladek%20has%20installed%20nearly%20500%20e-waste%20bins%2C%20not%20just%20as%20collection%20points%20but%20as%20visible%2C%20everyday%20reminders%20that%20electronic%20waste%20is%20real%20and%20needs%20attention.%20These%20bins%2C%20placed%20in%20schools%2C%20offices%2C%20and%20public%20spaces%2C%20have%20become%20quiet%20markers%20of%20a%20larger%20mission%3A%20to%20make%20e-waste%20visible%2C%20understood%2C%20and%20acted%20upon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20a%20smooth%20path.%20The%20road%20to%20awareness%2C%20as%20Priyasha%20Singhania%20shares%2C%20has%20been%20long%20and%20layered.%20%E2%80%9CAwareness%20about%20biodegradable%20and%20non-biodegradable%20waste%20was%20high%2C%20but%20e-waste%20was%20being%20overlooked%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20Executive%20Vice%20President%2C%20Branding%20and%20Communication.%20Her%20words%20reflect%20a%20national%20blind%20spot%E2%80%94a%20collective%20unawareness%20of%20the%20toxins%20hiding%20in%20our%20broken%20gadgets%20and%20discarded%20electronics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%2