cling%20continues%20to%20confront%20is%20the%20perception%20that%20equates%20recyclers%20with%20local%20scrap%20dealers.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20misconception%20that%20undermines%20the%20scale%20and%20seriousness%20of%20their%20work.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20often%20mistake%20us%20for%20just%20another%20scrap%20dealer%2C%20whereas%20we%20operate%20with%20government-approved%20systems%20and%20documentation%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Priyasha.%20Changing%20this%20mindset%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20easy%2C%20but%20Hulladek%20has%20met%20it%20head-on.%20They%E2%80%99ve%20worked%20relentlessly%20through%20persistent%20educational%20outreach%20and%20years%20of%20steady%20community%20engagement%20to%20rebuild%20trust%20and%20establish%20credibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHulladek%20has%20joined%20hands%20with%20state%20pollution%20control%20boards%20in%20Punjab%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Andaman%2C%20Assam%2C%20Nagaland%2C%20and%20Gujarat%20to%20amplify%20this%20effort.%20These%20partnerships%20are%20not%20symbolic%E2%80%94they%20serve%20as%20the%20foundation%20for%20grassroots%20change.%20By%20training%20board%20members%20and%20sensitising%20citizens%2C%20the%20company%20is%20helping%20communities%20understand%20what%E2%80%99s%20at%20stake%20and%20equipping%20them%20with%20the%20tools%20to%20take%20meaningful%20action%20against%20unsafe%20e-waste%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Hulladek%20manages%20e-waste%20collection%20for%20over%20300%20contract-based%20clients%2C%20including%20schools%2C%20colleges%2C%20and%20corporations%2C%20each%20one%20a%20step%20closer%20to%20a%20cleaner%2C%20safer%20system.%20Among%20them%20is%20GTPL%20KCPL%2C%20a%20major%20player%20managing%20a%20staggering%2040%20lakh%20cable%20TV%20boxes.%20Their%20director%2C%20Ankit%20Agarwal%2C%20acknowledges%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20partnership%2C%20further%20underlining%20Hulladek%E2%80%99s%20growing%20role%20in%20shaping%20responsible%20e-waste%20management%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-