C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20decision%20was%20driven%20by%20a%20conviction%20to%20protect%20the%20ecosystem%20and%20uphold%20our%20corporate%20social%20responsibility.%20Apart%20from%20financial%20gain%20from%20selling%20scrap%2C%20we%20now%20have%20assurance%20that%20our%20e-waste%20is%20managed%20ethically.%20Recycling%20ensures%20that%20resources%20that%20would%20have%20ended%20up%20in%20landfills%20are%20reused.%20As%20companies%20become%20more%20aware%2C%20these%20efforts%20encourage%20a%20more%20sustainable%20business%20environment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20true%20power%20of%20waste%20lies%20in%20what%20we%20teach%20the%20next%20generation%20to%20do%20with%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20Hulladek%20Recycling%20has%20helped%20divert%20more%20than%2025%20million%20kilograms%20of%20waste%20away%20from%20landfills%2C%20polluted%20waterways%2C%20and%20unsafe%20dumping%20grounds.%20This%20includes%20an%20astonishing%2015%20million%20kilograms%20of%20e-waste%E2%80%94a%20mix%20of%20everyday%20items%20like%20remote%20controls%2C%20hair%20straighteners%2C%20and%20large-scale%20appliances%20such%20as%20transformers%20and%20ATMs.%20Behind%20every%20kilogram%20is%20a%20moment%20of%20choice%3A%20to%20discard%20thoughtlessly%2C%20or%20to%20recycle%20responsibly.%20Hulladek%20is%20working%20to%20ensure%20that%20more%20people%20choose%20the%20latter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20life%20gives%20you%20lemonade%2C%20we%20make%20lemons.%20That%E2%80%99s%20recycling%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nandan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20numbers%20reflect%20growth%2C%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20more%20resounding%20success%20lies%20in%20its%20purpose.%20In%20the%20last%20financial%20year%2C%20Hulladek%20reported%20an%20annual%20turnover%20of%20%E2%82%B920%20crore%2C%20with%20a%20profit%20margin%20of%20at%20least%20five%20percent.%20Yet%20for%20founder%20Nandan%2C%20impact%20is%20not%20just%20financial%2C%