%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOur%20DRE%20system%20batteries%20come%20with%20a%20warranty%20of%20five%20years%20as%20mandated%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20New%20and%20Renewable%20Energy%20(MNRE)%3B%20if%20maintained%20very%20well%2C%20they%20run%20for%20about%20eight%20to%20ten%20years.%20Panels%20also%20come%20with%20a%20similar%20warranty%2C%20but%20they%20typically%20last%20about%2020%E2%80%9325%20years.%20Hence%2C%20capacity%20building%20for%20maintenance%20is%20a%20core%20focus%20area.%20It%20includes%20pre-installation%2C%20installation%2C%20and%20post-installation%20training%20for%20local%20enterprises%20and%20technicians.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20cannot%20expect%20anyone%20to%20provide%20this%20service%20for%20free.%20So%2C%20we%20prioritise%20local%20enterprises%20with%20a%20good%20service%20network%20to%20install%20the%20systems%2C%20and%20the%20payment%20comes%2C%20and%20this%20is%20a%20systemic%20innovation%2C%20from%20untied%20funds%20with%20local%20Rogi%20Kalyan%20Samitis.%20These%20are%20patient%20welfare%20committees%20enabled%20by%20the%20NHM%20(National%20Health%20Mission)%20that%20act%20as%20trustees%20for%20hospitals%20and%20health%20centres.%20They%20are%20free%20to%20prescribe%2C%20generate%2C%20and%20use%20their%20funds%20as%20per%20their%20judgment%20for%20the%20smooth%20functioning%20and%20maintenance%20of%20the%20services.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EE4H%20DRE%20systems%20have%20a%20standard%20built-in%20autonomy%20of%20two%20to%20three%20days%2C%20but%20if%20we%20implement%20them%20in%20an%20area%20with%20very%20heavy%20rainfall%20or%20high%20cloud%20cover%2C%20we%20extend%20it%20to%20five%20to%20six%20days.%20If%20our%20systems%20can%20function%2